com.usebottles.bottles (2021.7.2-treviso) precise; urgency=low

  * New versioning based on CalVer model
  * Create bottles using the wine runner provided by the distribution
  * Enable gamemode for your bottles if installed in the system
  * Run .exe/.msi/.bat files with custom arguments
  * Fixed the "bad interpreter" error on debian package
  * Optionally close Bottles after starting an executable from the file manager
  * Added tooltips to understand what some elements of the UI do
  * Using portal for file picker
  * Filechooser do not filter by extensions anymore
  * Esperanto translations thanks to @phlostically
  * Spanish translations thanks to @fitojb
  * Croatin translations thanks to @milotype
  * Portuguese translations thanks to @laralem
  * French translations thanks to @julroy67
  * Swedish translations thanks to @eson57
  * Ukrain thanslations thanks to @marchellodev


